</id><title>葉秀亮不停唱衰香港市道，遲早被封殺滅聲！</title><updated>2025-08-23T08:39:35+08:00</updated><author><name>okla3</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-23T08:39:35+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573701351"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573701351"&gt;成日話香港有排仆街冚家剷&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32014154&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=113596862368a920143216f0_01932452"/><published>2025-08-23T08:39:35+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f386cc96ef5a9639601b8bfbeaae6c6b</id><title>收租王永倫以7600萬再沽長沙灣護老院</title><updated>2025-08-23T09:47:14+08:00</updated><author><name>okla3</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-23T09:47:14+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573702065"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573702065"&gt;回報8.3厘都不俗，市況離底應不遠&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32014206&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=113596862368a920143216f0_01932452"/><published>2025-08-23T09:47:14+08:00</published></entry></feed>